node.nodeValue);\\n        }\\n        // copy element styles to the wrapper\\n        wrapper.style.cssText = element.style.cssText;\\n        return wrapper;\\n      }\\n\\n      /**\\n       * = ownerDocument.parentWindow;\\n\\n        if (!supportsShivableSheets || ownerDocument.printShived) {\\n          return ownerDocument;\\n        }\\n        if (typeof namespaces[shivNamespace] == node.nodeValue);\\n        }\\n        // copy element styles to the wrapper\\n        wrapper.style.cssText = element.style.cssText;\\n        return wrapper;\\n      }\\n\\n      /**\\n       * = ownerDocument.parentWindow;\\n\\n        if (!supportsShivableSheets || ownerDocument.printShived) {\\n          return ownerDocument;\\n        }\\n        if (typeof namespaces[shivNamespace] ==
